  <brief_title>A 6-Month Consumer Behavior Study of a Self-Management System (0803-084)(COMPLETED)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Consumer Use Study of OTC Lovastatin (CUSTOM): A 6-Month Consumer Behavior Study of the Lovastatin OTC Self-Management System</official_title>
  <sponsors>
