  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the ability of patients with intermediate risk of
      heart disease to appropriately use a Self-Management System.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The duration of treatment is 6 months.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
